columns.name: PARTY_SITE_GID
columns.description: The GID for the party site associated with the GTM campaign line.

columns.name: IS_QUALIFIED
columns.description: Indicates if an item qualified for a trade agreement. Can have 'Y','N', 'NS' and 'D', where Y is Yes, N is No, NS is Not Started, and D is Discontinued. The default value is 'NS'

columns.name: QF_PREFERENCE_CRITERIA_GID
columns.description: The GID for the preference criteria related to the trade program for which the goods qualify.

columns.name: QF_RVC_METHOD_GID
columns.description: The GID for the regional value content method related to the trade program for which the goods qualify.

columns.name: PRODUCER
columns.description: Indicates the producer of the goods.

columns.name: QF_EFFECTIVE_DATE
columns.description: The date on which the qualification for a trade program is effective.

columns.name: QF_EXPIRATION_DATE
columns.description: The date on which the qualification for a trade program expires.

columns.name: COUNTRY_OF_ORIGIN
columns.description: The country of origin of the goods on the campaign line.

columns.name: ORIGIN_EFFECTIVE_DATE
columns.description: The date on which the country of origin is effective.

columns.name: ORIGIN_EXPIRATION_DATE
columns.description: The date on which the country of origin expires.

columns.name: ITEM_GID
columns.description: This column stores the Item GID for which the Campaign Line is created.
